<br>
<br>
What probably happened is you cleaned out your vault one day and accidently deleted it. Maybe you noticed it maybe you didnt but the GM is not required to replace it for you. Thats the bottom line. Sony has made some exceptions in the recent past at replacing items lost but given no timeframe other than &quot;Sometime between January and Now&quot; your literally talking about a massive hunt for an item on your account. Sony is religious about backups but comon man. 1 yr??<br>
<br>
Also expecting the GM to just reset your faction because somehow it got lowered is a bit much. in 1 yrs time there are several npc's thruout the game world who can lower your status with truespirit. Its your fault you took a year away from your epic. Not Sony's. Id have to side with them on that. Be thankful they implemented a quest to reset it. I know plenty of wizard friends in the past who literally were SOL.<br>
<br>
<br>
